@cfbayern: &quot;Klopp had a zoom call with Timo, he explained his plans, but at the time we didn&rsquo;t know what will happen [w/ COVID], he promised to develop him, &amp; told him that when AFCON came he&rsquo;ll play a lot, but [later] the money wasn&rsquo;t there for #LFC, and AFCON got postponed&quot;<br />
<br />
 @cfbayern: &quot;...things were happening very quick, Chelsea had the money and Timo didn&rsquo;t want to wait again, last summer he waited too long for Bayern [no offer], and he couldn&rsquo;t wait [again] for #LFC, for him was also nice because at Chelsea he knew he will play [consistently]&quot;<br />
<br />
@cfbayern: &quot;Klopp believes in Thiago, there is a connection, we know he [Klopp] placed Thiago&rsquo;s name on the board. There&rsquo;s not so many players of the level of Thiago in #LFC&rsquo;s midfield, so they have to do something in midfield. Thiago&rsquo;s first option is of course Liverpool!&quot;<br />
<br />
